2. Support the immediate release of all political detainees who peacefully demonstrated against Albashirxs regime;
3. Side with the people of Sudan and support their revolution to end the era of Albashirxs cruel, brutal, and corrupt regime;
4. Help the people of Sudan to arrest, seize Albashir and other officials indicted for committing genocide, human rights violations, war crimes, and hand them to the International Criminal Court (ICC).
